{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 70,
  "title": "第七十章（知難）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "章吾言甚易知，甚易行。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天下莫能知，莫能行。"
    },
    {
      "text": "言有宗，事有君。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯無知，是以不我知。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知我者希，則我者貴。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人被褐懷玉。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "老子言：吾所言省而易知，約而易行。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人惡柔弱，好剛強也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我所言有宗祖根本，事有君臣上下，世人不知者，非我之無德，心與我之反也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫唯世人之無知者，是我德之暗，不見於外，窮微極妙，故無知也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "希，少也。唯達道者乃能知我，故為貴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "被褐者薄外，懷玉者厚內，匿寶藏德，不以示人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
